{"tid":1197950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去完遊行之後發咗個夢","createTime":"2019-06-10T06:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T10:34:08.000Z","uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b5024c3ac76305918e9f6a40a22dca0501cc565","tid":1197950,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"夢入面見到,幾車豬幾車牛出現喺街頭上 , 曱甴爬嚟爬去 , 著藍色衫嘅......比人曱甴搞到痕死。<br />\n方陣圓陣都畀老鼠曱甴搞到大亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲豬當正條街喺屋企 ,阻塞咗交通 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n牛就去咗附近草地食草不過<br />\n唔知點解睇嚟好嬲, 眼神好兇惡, <br />\n可能太耐冇做運動想跑嚟跑去啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外, 地面同埋天空中<br />\n曱甴,蛤拐, 老鼠, 蟑螂 , 蝗蟲,<br />\n蜘蛛, 蝙蝠, 都出曬嚟<br />\n成個情況好可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n, 仲見到好似有人同佢哋大戰添,<br />\n好似啲科幻電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係慘連啲昆蟲都走上街頭,社會應付<br />\n人都唔掂仲要應對動物昆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, <br />\n佢哋仲要特別鍾情於藍色嘅添, <br />\n反而好怕白色,見到白色嘅就即刻走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 <br />\n着住藍衫嘅人,真係戥佢哋可憐,<br />\n畀曱由搞到好痕, 見到都覺得驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d37330d2f0eb2c861f0aac0c9ebd856f5ee24b7","tid":1197950,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:06:43.000Z","msg":"有冇解夢人 ,夢入面可以為我<br />\n哋帶到啲咩<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">啟示</span></span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">[size=6] 策略</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9415addd7bb948404c68361a778d338d9449c7ee","tid":1197950,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:32:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5929446fde6dabdb2dfdacb29abe6381844acc09","tid":1197950,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:34:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}